#### 1.5 — Expand / Reduce Trip Days

##### [MODIFY] [DayTabs.tsx](file:///Users/sadmanshaharier/Documents/ProjectOdyssey/client/odyssey/app/planner2/components/DayTabs.tsx)
- Add `onAddDay?: () => void` and `onRemoveDay?: () => void` props
- Render a "+" button after the last day tab and a "−" button (only if days > 1)

##### [MODIFY] [page.tsx (planner2)](file:///Users/sadmanshaharier/Documents/ProjectOdyssey/client/odyssey/app/planner2/page.tsx)
- Add `handleAddDay()` — increments `activeTrip.days`, adds empty schedule entry, persists to backend
- Add `handleRemoveDay()` — decrements `activeTrip.days`, removes last day's schedule, persists to backend
- Pass these as callbacks to [DayTabs](file:///Users/sadmanshaharier/Documents/ProjectOdyssey/client/odyssey/app/planner2/components/DayTabs.tsx#11-31)

