#### 1.6 — Print Plan

##### [NEW] [PrintView.tsx](file:///Users/sadmanshaharier/Documents/ProjectOdyssey/client/odyssey/app/planner2/components/PrintView.tsx)
- A print-optimized component that renders the full trip schedule in a clean, paginated layout
- Each day gets its own section with items listed as a table: Time | Place | Duration | Category
- Uses `@media print` CSS for clean output
- Triggered via a "Print" button in the planner top bar

##### [MODIFY] [page.tsx (planner2)](file:///Users/sadmanshaharier/Documents/ProjectOdyssey/client/odyssey/app/planner2/page.tsx)
- Add `showPrintView` state and a "🖨 Print" button in the top bar
- When toggled, render `PrintView` in a full-screen overlay, and call `window.print()`

