### Phase 2: Trip Mode Fixes

---

#### 2.1 — Load Active Plan (Not Mock / Latest)

##### [MODIFY] [page.tsx (trip)](file:///Users/sadmanshaharier/Documents/ProjectOdyssey/client/odyssey/app/trip/page.tsx)
- Change [loadSavedItinerary](file:///Users/sadmanshaharier/Documents/ProjectOdyssey/client/odyssey/app/trip/page.tsx#64-130): Instead of grabbing `data.data[0]` (latest trip), find the trip with `status === "active"`
- Fallback: if no active trip, show a message "No active trip. Go to Planner and activate a trip."
- Normalize schedule: Handle both `Record<number, Item[]>` and `Array<{day, items}>` formats (matching planner's [normalizeSchedule](file:///Users/sadmanshaharier/Documents/ProjectOdyssey/client/odyssey/app/planner2/page.tsx#197-246))

