#### 2.5 — Fix Checkout & Generic Location Handling

##### [MODIFY] [page.tsx (trip)](file:///Users/sadmanshaharier/Documents/ProjectOdyssey/client/odyssey/app/trip/page.tsx)
- In the Navigate link: if `item.placeId` is missing, fall back to `lat,lng` coordinates in the Google Maps URL
